reator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"Steven Zahm";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2980:"<p>Tile Plus has received a significant update to take full advantage of all the newer features built into Connections.</p>\n<div class="note"><h4 class="note_title">Important</h4><div class="note_content">Tile Plus 3.0 takes advantage of the new and improved template system introduced in version 0.7.6 of Connections. Please read the following installation instructions.</p>\n<p>If you are upgrading from an older version of Tile Plus you must go to the Connections : Templates admin page and delete the older version before installing the new version.</p>\n<p>To install the new version, please install it as you would any plugin, please do not use the template installer found on the Connections : Templates admin page. The template installer will only remain in place until all templates have been updated to use the new templating system. After which it will be removed completely.</p>\n<p>After you install Tile Plus, as a plugin, activate it as a plugin.</p>\n<p>Finally, Tile Plus will show up on the Connections : Templates admin page and be available for use.</div></div>\n<div class="clearboth"></div>\n<div class="one_third"></div> <div class="one_third"></div> <div class="one_third last">		<!--dynamic-cached-content-->\n		<form id="edd_purchase_2719" class="edd_download_purchase_form" method="post">\n\n			\n			<div class="edd_purchase_submit_wrapper">\n\n				<span class="edd_button_shell edd_color_royalgreen"><a href="#" class="edd-add-to-cart " data-action="edd_add_to_cart" data-download-id="2719" data-variable-price=no data-price-mode=single ><span class="edd-add-to-cart-label">&#036;19.99&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;Add to Cart</span> <span class="edd-loading"><i class="edd-icon-spinner edd-icon-spin"></i></span></a><input type="subm