n place until all templates have been updated to use the new templating system. After which it will be removed completely.</p>\n<p>After you install cMap, as a plugin, activate it as a plugin.</p>\n<p>Finally, after cMap has been activated, it will show up on the Connections : Templates admin page and be available for use.</div></div>\n<div class="clearboth"></div>\n<div class="one_third"></div> <div class="one_third"></div> <div class="one_third last">		<!--dynamic-cached-content-->\n		<form id="edd_purchase_2709" class="edd_download_purchase_form" method="post">\n\n			\n			<div class="edd_purchase_submit_wrapper">\n\n				<span class="edd_button_shell edd_color_royalgreen"><a href="#" class="edd-add-to-cart " data-action="edd_add_to_cart" data-download-id="2709" data-variable-price=no data-price-mode=single ><span class="edd-add-to-cart-label">&#036;19.99&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;Add to Cart</span> <span class="edd-loading"><i class="edd-icon-spinner edd-icon-spin"></i></span></a><input type="submit" class="edd-add-to-cart edd-no-js " name="edd_purchase_download" value="&#036;19.99&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;Add to Cart" data-action="edd_add_to_cart" data-download-id="2709" data-variable-price=no data-price-mode=single /><a href="https://connections-pro.com/shopping-cart/" class="edd_go_to_checkout button" style="display:none;">Checkout</a></span><!--end .edd_button_shell-->\n									<span class="edd-cart-ajax-alert">\n						<div><span class="edd-cart-added-alert" style="display: none;">\n							<i class="edd-icon-ok"></i> Item added to cart.						</span></div>\n					</span>\n				\n			</div><!--end .edd_purchase_submit_wrapper-->\n\n			\n			<input type="hidden" name="download_id" value="2709">\n							<input type="hidden" name="edd_action" class="edd_action_input" value="add_to_cart">\n			\n			\n		</form><!--end #edd_purchase_2709-->\n		<!--/dynamic-cached-content-->\n	</div><div class="clearboth"></div>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://connections-pro.com/2013/03/25/t