 sure to delete it first.</li>\n<li>And lastly, the number one feature request, an easy way to change the color. Here&#8217;s a few examples:</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Slim in its default blue:</p>\n<div id="cn-top" style="position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0;"></div><div class="cn-list" id="cn-list" data-connections-version="8.1.5-0.1.9"><div class="cn-template cn-slim" id="cn-slim" data-template-version="3.0">\n<div class="cn-list-head cn-clear" id="cn-list-head">\n\n</div>\n\n<div class="connections-list cn-list-body cn-clear" id="cn-list-body">\n<div class="cn-list-section-head" id="cn-char-D"></div><div class="cn-list-row-alternate vcard individual uncategorized" id="jane-doe-2" data-entry-type="individual" data-entry-id="195" data-entry-slug="jane-doe-2">\n<div id="entry-id-1955486aae48507f" class="cn-entry">\n\n	<h3 class="cn-accordion-item" data-div-id="cn-detail-1955486aae48507f" style="border-bottom: #00508D 1px solid; color:#00508D;"><span class="cn-sprite" style="background-color: #00508D;"></span>\n<span class="fn n"> <span class="given-name">Jane</span> <span class="family-name">Doe</span> </span>\n</h3><div class="cn-detail cn-clear cn-hide" id="cn-detail-1955486aae48507f"><div class="cn-left">\n<span class="cn-image-style" style="display: inline-block;"><span class="cn-image-photo cn-image-none" style="width: 100px; height: 120px; display: inline-block;"><span>No Photo Available</span></span></span>\n</div><div class="cn-right">\n<span class="address-block">\n<span class="adr"><span class="address-name">Home</span> <span class="street-address">123 Sample Street</span> <span class="locality">Lancaster</span> <span class="region">PA</span> <span class="postal-code">12345</span> <span class="type" style="display: none;">home</span></span>\n</span>\n\n<span class="phone-number-block">\n<span class="tel"><span class="phone-name">Cell Phone</span><span class="cn-separator">:</span> <span class="value">717-555-1235</span><span class="type" style="display: none;">cell